        "action": "Reject any proposals to abolish District Councils in Lancashire",
        "additional_details": "The proposal by Geoff Driver The Leader of Lancashire County Council, has not had engagement with the Leaders of Lancashire\u2019s councils and more importantly the community in a manner of mutual respect through engagement. The community must have a say in regard to the Future of Local Government in Lancashire.",
        "background": "We call upon Parliament and Government to reject any proposals in regard to Lancaster District Council being merged within a Newly Formed Unitary Authority with Blackpool.",
